Subject: [PATCH 0708/1543] ENGR00332050-2 imx_v7_defconfig: enable ADC driver
 by default

commit cd9252d9193af5d39200745b0ee8f7bc8a189712 from
git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git

